      <title>土耳其 10 月份贸易逆差收窄 13%，进口降幅放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-02/turkey-trade-deficit-narrows-13-in-october-import-drop-slows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其 10 月份贸易逆差为 57.5 亿美元，进一步收窄表明该国经济的再平衡仍在进行中。进口降幅为过去六个月以来最慢，反映出土耳其里拉的相对强势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-02/turkey-trade-deficit-narrows-13-in-october-import-drop-slows</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 02 Nov 2024 09:48:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国不稳定的执政联盟面临 750 亿欧元的预算清算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-02/german-government-budget-shaky-coalition-heads-for-75-billion-reckoning</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国政府正准备迎接一项至关重要的法庭裁决，该裁决可能会剥夺国库高达 750 亿欧元（820 亿美元）的税收收入，并可能在距离选举仅剩一年的情况下使陷入困境的联盟政府陷入危险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-02/german-government-budget-shaky-coalition-heads-for-75-billion-reckoning</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 02 Nov 2024 08:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>TGI Friday’s 成为最新一家破产的休闲餐饮连锁店</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-02/tgi-friday-s-becomes-latest-casual-dining-chain-to-go-bankrupt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[休闲餐饮连锁店 TGI Friday’s Inc. 申请破产保护，原因是难以扭转业务困境，受到越来越注重成本的消费者的压力，这些消费者在外出就餐时要么变得更加挑剔，要么更喜欢提供快餐的竞争对手。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-02/tgi-friday-s-becomes-latest-casual-dining-chain-to-go-bankrupt</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 02 Nov 2024 07:24:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
